Today I have upgraded R to version 4.2 on Windows and it was no pain at all!!!
It's probably worth to share some code (maybe not perfect but I think it's good enough)
#rstats #nflverse
https://t.co/xG84Q1EInz https://t.co/HUK3eI7wQk

Last 10 years of Patriots and Seahawks Drafts. Belichick chose best in the late first round and in the fourth / fifth rounds. Carroll was better in the second and third rounds. 

#nflverse @pfref https://t.co/4wYKjgib8h

cool nflreadr stuff on the horizon: a oneliner to mass download some or all of the #nflverse releases (in your preferred format!) to a local folder. 

Here's "all of nflverse-data in parquet format" in two minutes: https://t.co/ZRaZJgh6ly

Truly unfortunate that the Chargers have to play the Chiefs in week 2 since Patrick Mahomes in the first quarter of the season is one of the scariest things in all of football.

#nflverse https://t.co/PDxFa33Npf https://t.co/RKhE2J5YuM
